ence\": \"Sports manager Danny Stam confirmed the Belgian's participation speaking toHet Laatste Nieuws, with a decision to be made on the French Grand Tour after she makes her debut at Li\\u00e8ge-Bastogne-Li\\u00e8ge Femmes on April 21.\", \"from\": 575, \"to\": 791, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 590, \"end\": 600, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Danny_Stam\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Danny Stam\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Danny_Stam\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Danny_Stam\"}, {\"begin\": 615, \"end\": 622, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium\", \"score\": 0.9998949661661657, \"rank\": 9.167414540517017e-05, \"text\": \"Belgian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium\"}, {\"begin\": 704, \"end\": 710, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.8865231766012999, \"rank\": 0.128001120403392, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 711, \"end\": 721, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grand_Tour\", \"score\": 0.9982983105492684, \"rank\": 0.00170459013370492, \"text\": \"Grand Tour\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grand_Tour\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grand_Tour\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Lotte [Kopecky] will ride the Giro.\", \"from\": 793, \"to\": 829, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"An ideal race to score and improve stage wins yourself,\\\" Stam told the Belgian newspaper.\", \"from\": 830, \"to\": 919, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 901, \"end\": 908, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium\", \"score\": 0.9998949661661657, \"rank\": 9.167414540517017e-05, \"text\": \"Belgian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There is no long list for the Tour yet because certain riders are injured and it is not yet clear whether they will be fit.\", \"from\": 921, \"to\": 1045, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"After Li\\u00e8ge, I will sit down with Lotte and talk about the Tour.\", \"from\": 1046, \"to\": 1110, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1052, \"end\": 1057, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Li\\u00e8ge\", \"score\": 0.9918545502535505, \"rank\": 0.005035105293388885, \"text\": \"Li\\u00e8ge\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Li\\u00e8ge\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Li\\u00e8ge\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The most important thing is what she wants.\\\"\", \"from\": 1111, \"to\": 1155, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The best in the world?\", \"from\": 1157, \"to\": 1179, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Lotte Kopecky stays modest after storming to Paris-Roubaix victory'We wanted to keep them both' - SD Worx did not favour Kopecky over Vollering for 2025World champion Lotte Kopecky aims high in 2024 with Paris-Roubaix, Olympic goals  Kopecky was imperious at the Tour in 2023 as she won the opening stage, claimed the green points jersey and finished second overall behind teammate Demi Vollering.\", \"from\": 1180, \"to\": 1577, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1180, \"end\": 1193, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lotte_Kopecky\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lotte Kopecky\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lotte_Kopecky\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lotte_Kopecky\"}, {\"begin\": 1225, \"end\": 1238, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\\u2013Roubaix\", \"score\": 0.9816675037644488, \"rank\": 0.004431782209560121, \"text\": \"Paris-Roubaix\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\", \"Q15091377\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\\u2013Roubaix\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\\u2013Roubaix\"}, {\"begin\": 1347, \"end\": 1360, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lotte_Kopecky\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lotte Kopecky\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lotte_Kopecky\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lotte_Kopecky\"}, {\"begin\": 1562, \"end\": 1576, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Demi_Vollering\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Demi Vollering\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Demi_Vollering\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Demi_Vollering\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, she's been doubtful about her participation ever since the dates and route were announced last year, due to close scheduling with the Omnium track event at the Olympics.\", \"from\": 1579, \"to\": 1757, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The last of four Omnium races finishes on August 11, just one day before the start of theTour de France Femmesin Rotterdam.\", \"from\": 1759, \"to\": 1882, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1856, \"end\": 1862, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9182601824228062, \"rank\": 0.08177646913270796, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1872, \"end\": 1881, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rotterdam\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1262212697453214e-16, \"text\": \"Rotterdam\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rotterdam\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rotterdam\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Kopecky definitely wants to ride, but conceded in October that \\\"the Tour is every year while the Olympic Games are only once every four years\\\", making it a tough decision.\", \"from\": 1883, \"to\": 2054, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The latest race content, interviews, features, reviews and expert buying guides, direct to your inbox!\", \"from\": 2056, \"to\": 2158, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In contrast, the rebranded Giro d'Italia Women fits perfectly with Kopecky's Olympic goals, running from July 7-14 for eight stages of racing.\", \"from\": 2160, \"to\": 2302, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2187, \"end\": 2200, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Giro_d'Italia\", \"score\": 0.9999999999822649, \"rank\": 1.7389436671035313e-11, \"text\": \"Giro d'Italia\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\", \"Q15091377\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Giro_d'Italia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Giro_d'Italia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This would give Kopecky three weeks to reach her absolute peak for the Olympic road race in Paris on August 4.\", \"from\": 2303, \"to\": 2413, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2395, \"end\": 2400, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.387068758626627e-14, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She missed the Italian stage race in 2023 but has raced it there in 2019, 2020 and 2022.\", \"from\": 2415, \"to\": 2503, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2430, \"end\": 2437, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_language\", \"score\": 0.6533646472521567, \"rank\": 0.5305357355388608, \"text\": \"Italian\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Giro was also where she took her first of many WorldTour wins on stage 7 four years ago while still riding for Lotto Soudal.\", \"from\": 2504, \"to\": 2632, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2619, \"end\": 2624, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lottery\", \"score\": 0.999999999650754, \"rank\": 3.4927388296090747e-10, \"text\": \"Lotto\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lottery\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lottery\"}, {\"begin\": 2625, \"end\": 2631, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Soudal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Soudal\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Soudal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Soudal\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Fresh off the back of herthrilling Paris-Roubaix victory, Kopecky is next in action during the Ardennes Classics at the Amstel Gold Race and Li\\u00e8ge.\", \"from\": 2634, \"to\": 2781, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2669, \"end\": 2682, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\\u2013Roubaix\", \"score\": 0.9816675037644488, \"rank\": 0.004431782209560121, \"text\": \"Paris-Roubaix\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\", \"Q15091377\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\\u2013Roubaix\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\\u2013Roubaix\"}, {\"begin\": 2729, \"end\": 2737, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ardennes_classics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.829494881951238e-14, \"text\": \"Ardennes\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ardennes_classics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ardennes_classics\"}, {\"begin\": 2738, \"end\": 2746, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Classic_cycle_races\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4308923038899045e-52, \"text\": \"Classics\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Classic_cycle_races\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Classic_cycle_races\"}, {\"begin\": 2775, \"end\": 2780, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Li\\u00e8ge\", \"score\": 0.9918545502535505, \"rank\": 0.005035105293388885, \"text\": \"Li\\u00e8ge\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Li\\u00e8ge\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Li\\u00e8ge\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite Kopecky being the long-term project at SD Worx-Protime having signed a contract extension until 2028 withVollering set to depart the team in 2025, \\u00a0she will play second fiddle to her Dutch teammate in the hilly Classics.\", \"from\": 2783, \"to\": 3011, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2974, \"end\": 2979, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"score\": 0.9994101018966552, \"rank\": 0.0005902312125475773, \"text\": \"Dutch\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Demi is our leader in the Ardennes.\", \"from\": 3013, \"to\": 3049, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3040, \"end\": 3048, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ardennes_classics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.829494881951238e-14, \"text\": \"Ardennes\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ardennes_classics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ardennes_classics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We hope to win at least one victory with her,\\\" Stam said.\", \"from\": 3050, \"to\": 3107, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"From now on, Demi is the leading lady and Lotte is a shadow leading lady.\", \"from\": 3108, \"to\": 3182, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"An important role.\", \"from\": 3183, \"to\": 3201, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I still expect something from Lotte.\\\"\", \"from\": 3202, \"to\": 3239, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite missing out on a third consecutive Tour of Flanders, Stam assured that the season has already been a success for the World Champion with big wins added to her palmar\\u00e8s.\", \"from\": 3241, \"to\": 3417, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3366, \"end\": 3380, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_championship\", \"score\": 0.7773559471908452, \"rank\": 0.2863274251082011, \"text\": \"World Champion\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_championship\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_championship\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There was a lot of pressure on our team and Lotte as world champion, but she won Strade Bianche and Paris-Roubaix.\", \"from\": 3419, \"to\": 3534, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3501, \"end\": 3515, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Strade_Bianche\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.928298744687366e-14, \"text\": \"Strade Bianche\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\", \"Q15091377\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Strade_Bianche\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Strade_Bianche\"}, {\"begin\": 3520, \"end\": 3533, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\\u2013Roubaix\", \"score\": 0.9816675037644488, \"rank\": 0.004431782209560121, \"text\": \"Paris-Roubaix\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\", \"Q15091377\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\\u2013Roubaix\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\\u2013Roubaix\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Then you can call it a successful campaign,\\\" he said, before admitting that it is not the Ardennes' terrain that could be Kopecky's undoing, but her form after a tough Classics campaign.\", \"from\": 3535, \"to\": 3721, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3625, \"end\": 3633, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ardennes_classics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.829494881951238e-14, \"text\": \"Ardennes\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ardennes_classics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ardennes_classics\"}, {\"begin\": 3703, \"end\": 3711, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Classic_cycle_races\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4308923038899045e-52, \"text\": \"Classics\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Classic_cycle_races\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Classic_cycle_races\"}]}, {\"sentence\"